title: Is this a true message presented at the COVID-19 demonstration against Lockdown?
subtitle: In many different cities in the United States, demonstrators protested that the restrictions imposed by the COVID-19 Conference on social balance were unnecessary or had persisted for a very long time.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: "Your health is no more important than my freedom!" A message was presented on a car window in a protest calling for the easing of the COVID-19 restrictions on social balance.
